Hello. I'm composer MJ.
In a quiet forest, beneath the evening sky,  
a child and a puppy sit side by side, gazing into the peaceful distance.  
The breeze gently stirs the leaves, and the soft chirping of insects fills the air,  
as a delicate piano melody begins to flow quietly.

This video is a healing space where nature and music come together  
to calm your heart and guide you into deep, restful sleep.

At the end of a long day,  
even on restless nights,  
this gentle forest scene and its soothing sounds  
will stay by your side, quietly comforting your soul.

For those tired from sleepless nights,  
for those with a restless mind,
